  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] By suspending this Digimon, 1 of your Digimon may
    digivolve into a Digimon card with [Fairy] in one of its traits in the hand for
    the digivolution cost. When it would digivolve by this effect, reduce the digivolution
    cost by 2.'
